{{Use dmy dates|date=December 2014}} {{Infobox newspaper | name = Corriere del Ticino | logo = Corriere de Ticino.svg | image = | caption = | alt = | type = [[Daily newspaper]] | format = | owners = | founder = | publisher = | editor = | chiefeditor = | assoceditor = | maneditor = | newseditor = | managingeditordesign = | opeditor = | sportseditor = | photoeditor = | seniorstaff = | staff = | foundation = {{start date and age|1891}} | political = | language = [[Italian language|Italian]] | headquarters = [[Muzzano, Switzerland|Muzzano]], [[Ticino]], [[Switzerland]] | circulation = | sister newspapers = | ISSN = | oclc = 31672743 | website = [http://www.cdt.ch cdt.ch] (in [[Italian language|Italian]]) }}
'''''Corriere del Ticino''''' is a regional [[daily newspaper]] in the [[canton of Ticino]], [[Switzerland]].
==History and profile== ''Corriere del Ticino'' was established in 1891.<ref name=bbc4>{{cite news|title=The press in Switzerland|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/3703425.stm|accessdate=17 January 2015|work=BBC|date=17 May 2004}}</ref> The paper is published in the [[Italian language]] in [[Muzzano, Switzerland|Muzzano]], Ticino.<ref name=bbc4/>
In the early 1990s ''Corriere del Ticino'' had a circulation of 36,000 copies.<ref>{{cite book|author1=Pierre Musso|author2=Philippe Souêtre|author3=Lionel Levasseur|title=The Printed Press and Television in the Regions of Europe|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xXueScfbDrgC&pg=PA105|accessdate=27 December 2014|year=1995|publisher=Council of Europe|isbn=978-92-871-2807-2|page=105}}</ref> In 1997 the paper had a circulation of 37,742 copies.<ref>{{cite journal|author=Sibylle Hardmeier|title=Political Poll Reporting in Swiss Print Media|journal=International Journal of Public Opinion Research|date=1999|volume=11|issue=3|url=http://ijpor.oxfordjournals.org/content/11/3/257.full.pdf|accessdate=30 December 2014}}</ref>
==See also== * ''[[LaNotizia]]'' * [[List of newspapers in Switzerland]]
