The '''Croatian Esperanto Leavue''' ([[Esperanto]]: ''Kroata Esperanto-Ligo'', '''KEL'''; [[Croatian language|Croatian]]: ''Hrvatski Savez za Esperanto'') is a society for those who speak Esperanto, Esperanto societies, and friends of Esperanto. It deals with Esperanto in Croatia.

It hosted the 86th [[World Esperanto Congress]] in [[Zagreb]] in 2001.

